Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Dialogue
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.37,0:00:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,这么晚了有事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.27,0:00:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 有点睡不着
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.93,0:00:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,看这样子 还是没找到那些护卫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.87,0:00:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.80,0:00:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,今天也找了一整天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.80,0:00:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道团长有发现什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.97,0:00:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,各位
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.27,0:00:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,团长应该不会出事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.23,0:02:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,这种时候居然还能避开要害
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.70,0:02:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,大介 你…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.90,0:02:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,风槌
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.43,0:02:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我的行动已经被看穿了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.67,0:03:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,吹散 风壁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.13,0:03:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,玷污了你副团长的身份
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.44,0:03:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,先睡会儿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.30,0:03:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,可恶 都让副团长帮忙了还这么惨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.80,0:03:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你只是这世界的人类而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.10,0:03:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么跟个怪物一样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.40,0:03:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,过奖了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.93,0:03:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是经验老道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.23,0:04:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,与人交战的经验老道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.60,0:04:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么还自豪起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.83,0:04:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,大介 你…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.90,0:04:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.87,0:04:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,他们到死也不会停下来的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.03,0:04:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,什么 你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.70,0:04:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么 明明闹出这么大动静
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.47,0:04:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么没人过来支援
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.17,0:04:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你就放弃挣扎去死吧 梅尔德团长
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.37,0:04:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.93,0:04:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我选择忍辱脱逃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.60,0:04:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.43,0:05:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,燃烧天地之红莲…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.77,0:05:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,不论是国王 还是骑士团
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.07,0:05:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,都太掉以轻心了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.17,0:05:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,毕竟只是一群人类
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.10,0:05:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,最后还是得靠我亲自出马
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.57,0:05:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,神大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.70,0:05:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.54,0:05:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是埃希德大人的旨意
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.27,0:05:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能说 接下来就靠你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.00,0:06:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,这可是你的敌人 所以
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.47,0:06:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,重拳出击！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.87,0:06:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,哎哟 不愧是团长大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.94,0:06:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,不得不说他办事真是万无一失
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.63,0:06:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,差点就被他得逞了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.37,0:06:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.90,0:06:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,说起来 你的伤怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.60,0:06:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,好像被揍得不轻吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.63,0:06:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,这点小伤算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.10,0:06:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,她呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.13,0:06:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,已经不见了 还说我们掉以轻心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.80,0:06:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.47,0:06:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,不过她的介入也在我们的计划之中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.77,0:06:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,毕竟我很有可能受了神之祝福
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.17,0:06:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,没想到还真有这么坏心眼的神
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.53,0:06:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,不论如何 最大的障碍已经扫除了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.90,0:06:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,之后只要不被八重檻她们发现
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.53,0:07:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,也就没什么问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.17,0:07:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.93,0:07:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,国王和宰相现在都跟灵魂出窍了一样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.83,0:07:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,教会一直以来也是毫无威胁
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.63,0:07:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.13,0:07:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,干掉团长之后 我们已经无人能挡了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.27,0:07:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧 加速吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.93,0:07:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,就像滚下山坡的大石头一样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.03,0:07:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,朝终点加速吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.83,0:07:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,朝我理想中的未来加速吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.23,0:07:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,缪送的贝壳能给我一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.20,0:07:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,可是可以
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.37,0:07:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,要用来干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.70,0:07:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,别问了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.20,0:07:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,咦 始大人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.83,0:08:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,那边是不是遭到袭击了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.80,0:08:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,对方好像是强盗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.40,0:08:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,有40来个衣衫不整的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.67,0:08:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,而护卫只有大概15个人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.63,0:08:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,战力差距这么大居然还能抗衡 挺厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.93,0:08:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 那个结界质量不错
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.30,0:08:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 不摧毁结界就无法靠近啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.77,0:08:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,隔着结界遭到魔法攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.70,0:08:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,强盗们肯定也气急败坏了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.60,0:08:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,不过 双方好像都不打算退让
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.73,0:08:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,那么大的结界
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.47,0:08:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,至少得是异世界组 不然撑不了多久
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.63,0:08:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,可能会花点时间 不过多等等就自己解除了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.67,0:08:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,始 帮帮忙 去救救他们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.50,0:08:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,说不定那边…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.33,0:09:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,始 谢谢…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.27,0:09:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,发现罪犯马上踩油门
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.20,0:09:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,驾校不就是这么教的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.15,0:09:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,才没这么教 你别乱改规定啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.47,0:09:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,什么情况
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.03,0:09:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,既然动手就不能手下留情 杀光他们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.33,0:09:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,没有慈悲可言
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.33,0:09:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道的吧 香织
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.13,0:09:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.80,0:09:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,那你去吧 没人敢妨碍你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.37,0:09:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.70,0:09:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,这臭婊子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.83,0:09:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,香织
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.40,0:10:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,果然 是莉莉对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.00,0:10:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我就觉得那个结界有点眼熟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.17,0:10:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,只是没想到你会出现在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.20,0:10:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我还有点半信半疑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.10,0:10:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,真是侥幸 看来我的运气还没用光
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.00,0:10:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,香织 治疗结束了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.20,0:10:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,是南云对吧 好久不见
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.23,0:10:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,雫她们说过你还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.80,0:10:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,没事就好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.60,0:10:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你不在的时候香织真是魂不守舍了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.87,0:10:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 现在就别提这些了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.70,0:10:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我还听说了香织一生难得的告白
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.50,0:10:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,待会儿一定要仔细说给我听听
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.80,0:11:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,话说 你谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.73,0:11:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,始 她是公主殿下 公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.93,0:11:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,海利希王国的公主 莉莉安娜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.37,0:11:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你忘了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.10,0:11:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,被人遗忘真是令人痛心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.47,0:11:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,莉莉 别哭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.20,0:11:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,始他只是有点那什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.43,0:11:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,一般人不可能忘记莉莉的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.10,0:11:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 你是不是偷偷在骂我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.83,0:11:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,所以 公主殿下来这种地方干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.33,0:11:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,莉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.67,0:11:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,爱子老师被抓走了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.80,0:12:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直觉得 王宫里的气氛有点不对劲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.57,0:12:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,父皇前所未有地专注于圣教教会
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.27,0:12:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,发疯似地崇拜埃希德大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.17,0:12:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,信仰无比坚定
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.07,0:12:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,起初 我以为他只是为了笼络圣教教会
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.93,0:12:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我心里的违和感始终没有消散
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.97,0:12:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,不久之后
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.90,0:12:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,大家就像生病了一样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.63,0:12:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,越来越多的骑士和士兵变得如同行尸走肉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.47,0:12:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,认定南云为异端分子的事情也是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.17,0:12:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,他们无视乌尔镇和奥尔库斯大迷宫的功劳
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.90,0:12:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,以及爱子老师的异议与反驳
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.13,0:12:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,当然 我向父皇提出了抗议
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.60,0:12:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,可不论我怎么说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.33,0:12:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,他都坚决认定南云是神的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.40,0:13:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,父皇看我的眼神也日渐充满了敌意
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.80,0:13:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我非常害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.63,0:13:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,想去找爱子老师谈谈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.73,0:13:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,结果爱子老师被神山的修女抓走了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.27,0:13:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,说不定修女就是这场异变的幕后黑手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.17,0:13:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,或者和幕后黑手有关
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.97,0:13:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我决定
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.70,0:13:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,必须把这件事告诉其他人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.10,0:13:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,但是王宫里面肯定已经被监视了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.10,0:13:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,所以只能找人帮忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.57,0:13:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我最先想到的 就是香织和南云
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.77,0:13:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,听雫说过你们往西走了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.20,0:13:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,接下来的事就如你们所见了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.67,0:13:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,为了得到杰根主公的支援
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.27,0:13:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我拜托队商的人 带我一起上路
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.90,0:13:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,没想到 中途居然能见到你们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.13,0:14:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,放在以前 我肯定会觉得这是神的保佑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.17,0:14:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我现在非常害怕教会
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.70,0:14:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,究竟发生什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.27,0:14:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,莉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.27,0:14:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,总之 得先去救老师才行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.43,0:14:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.20,0:14:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你别误会
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.17,0:14:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是为了你们王国 我只是去救老师
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.80,0:14:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,爱子老师吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.02,0:14:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,她被抓走也有我的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.53,0:14:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,不能放着她不管
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.60,0:14:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.57,0:14:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,如果救老师的过程中 异变的元凶出来阻挡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.63,0:14:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,不论对方是谁我都会送他归西
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.47,0:14:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,那就希望一切顺利吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.17,0:15:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托你了 南云
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.17,0:15:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,老师被带去的神山也是大迷宫之一
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.10,0:15:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,这次又能拿到什么神代魔法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.43,0:15:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,始 你真棒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.60,0:15:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,始大人又露出那种表情了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.77,0:15:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,真让人心跳加速
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.70,0:15:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,主人 见了你这副凶恶的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.60,0:15:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我会湿身的啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.33,0:16:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我的学生们想做的事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.93,0:16:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,究竟发生什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.83,0:16:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,扫清异种是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.07,0:16:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,异种…异种？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.73,0:16:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,南云
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.30,0:16:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,叫我干嘛 老师
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.83,0:16:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,这里 老师
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.47,0:16:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,是南云吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.43,0:16:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,这里可是最顶层 而且是在神山
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.17,0:16:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你先冷静点 老师
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.50,0:16:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,等我再确认一下有没有陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.30,0:17:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,有必要这么惊讶吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.80,0:17:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是已经注意到我来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.87,0:17:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,尽管我完全隐藏了气息
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.10,0:17:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,注意到了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.90,0:17:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是叫了我的名字吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.13,0:17:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,肯定是察觉到我的气息了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.83,0:17:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,话说回来 你为什么会来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.00,0:17:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,当然是来救你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.47,0:17:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,为了来救我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.07,0:17:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,特意来救我的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.93,0:17:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,不会已经被洗脑了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.93,0:17:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}为了我？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.53,0:17:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 不行 太突然了 我可是老师
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.97,0:17:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,不是 我只是帮你解开这个
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.60,0:17:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,魔力被封印了很不方便吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.22,0:17:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,还是说解开之后会出什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.33,0:18:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,原来是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.33,0:18:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你以为是要干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.03,0:18:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.23,0:18:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么知道我被抓了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.33,0:18:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,除了我应该没人…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.40,0:18:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,公主告诉我们的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.30,0:18:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,公主？莉莉安娜公主吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.23,0:18:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,她亲眼目睹了老师被抓走
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.53,0:18:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,之后 她认定王宫里已经被监视了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.83,0:18:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,不能去告诉天之河他们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.30,0:18:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,所以独自逃离了王都
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.53,0:18:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,寻求救援
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.20,0:18:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,原来是莉莉安娜公主
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.17,0:18:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你们帮助了她是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.47,0:18:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.33,0:18:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,闹成现在这样多半也有我的责任
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.50,0:19:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然老师可能不太想看见我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.17,0:19:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,和其他人汇合之前就先忍一忍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.18,0:19:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,不想见你是绝对不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.93,0:19:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,的确 清水同学的事情直到现在我也放不下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.37,0:19:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,今后 说不定很多事情我都放不下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.87,0:19:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 我也会理解你 当初究竟为何扣动扳机
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.30,0:19:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.33,0:19:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,当时没能认真说出口
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.20,0:19:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,趁现在让我好好说清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.00,0:19:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你救了我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.60,0:19:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,是我害你向同学扣动了扳机 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.77,0:20:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是按照我的想法行事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.00,0:20:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,道谢可以 道歉就不必了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.60,0:20:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,不说这些 该走了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.37,0:20:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,南云同学 当心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.63,0:20:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,教会已经完全认定你为异端分子了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.43,0:20:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,而且 抓走我的人说不定会把你…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.80,0:20:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道 总之把老师送回去之后
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.60,0:20:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我也还要办我的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.50,0:20:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,到时候应该也会和教会那些家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.20,0:20:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你早已下定决心了对吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.07,0:20:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.57,0:20:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,来得真是时候
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.23,0:20:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,某种意义上或许正合我意
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.87,0:20:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,发生什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.67,0:20:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,魔人族入侵了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.50,0:20:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,刚刚那应该是王都结界被破坏的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.87,0:21:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,魔人族入侵？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.80,0:21:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,就是说海利希王国正在遭受入侵
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.87,0:21:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.33,0:21:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,完全没料到这一手
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.87,0:21:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.97,0:21:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,老师 先和天之河他们汇合吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.27,0:21:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,之后再考虑这些
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.17,0:21:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.40,0:21:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,这是…被分解了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.40,0:21:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,回答正确
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.30,0:21:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,异种
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.87,0:21:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫诺因
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.10,0:21:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,身为神之使徒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.17,0:21:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我要为主人清除棋盘上多余的棋子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.07,0:23:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,下集 王都入侵
Comment: 0,0:00:41.94,0:00:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,-----------------OP-----------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.16,0:01:03.71,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}Tears streaming down your sorrow face
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.88,0:01:09.72,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}Came a long and painful road, you gave yourself away
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.55,0:01:15.05,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}You saw everything, heaven to hell
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.35,0:01:21.48,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}You say you need a self redemption, to mend the broken wings
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.98,0:01:26.90,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}Drowning in the dark, no place to be
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.61,0:01:30.65,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}But I am by your side
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.94,0:01:32.49,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}You’re not alone
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.74,0:01:38.41,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}Daylight, shed a light so you won’t disappear
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.62,0:01:44.37,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}Cause I know where you belong, save your saddened heart
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.37,0:01:50.09,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}With a flashback, screaming out but still we’re holding on
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.26,0:01:55.51,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}Waiting for the break of dawn for a new day to begin
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.97,0:01:58.76,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}Daylight, daylight
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.35,0:02:04.10,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}Stay a little while longer
Comment: 0,0:22:04.01,0:22:04.05,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,------------------ED------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.43,0:22:12.77,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}全部　期待してみて幻だった
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.77,0:22:17.27,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}信じたかった　縋りたかった
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.19,0:22:23.99,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}身体の底に開いた螺旋状の穴
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.28,0:22:29.16,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}ボクだけじゃなく　キミにもなんだね
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.62,0:22:38.34,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}許されることなど　もう望んじゃいない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.34,0:22:42.88,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}抱き寄せてもまた　わからないシルエット
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.88,0:22:47.43,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}躊躇いもなく傷つけた代償か
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.68,0:22:52.56,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}キミの側は　揺れてボクを離れた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.56,0:22:57.52,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}どちらが欲しいかなんて　残酷な問い神様は
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.52,0:23:02.11,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}何度ボクらに投げかける
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.11,0:23:07.11,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}道を違える度に　ボクの後ろに穴が開く
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.11,0:23:10.16,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}伸びた一本の影
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.45,0:23:16.62,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}誰もが手にし得る　小さな欠片で
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.87,0:23:21.21,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}何ができる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.21,0:23:26.38,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}どちらが欲しいかなんて　残酷な問い神様は
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.38,0:23:31.22,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}何度ボクらに投げかける
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.43,0:22:12.77,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}期待的一切皆为虚空一场
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.77,0:22:17.27,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}破灭的希望　虚伪的幻想
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.19,0:22:23.99,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嵌入身体的伤口深不见底
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.28,0:22:29.16,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不仅是我　你也背负同样的伤
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.62,0:22:38.34,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}早已不再奢望　求得谁人原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.34,0:22:42.88,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哪怕怀中相拥　徒留轮廓难辨
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.88,0:22:47.43,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}甘愿承伤不曾犹豫的代价
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.68,0:22:52.56,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我步履蹒跚　忍痛离开你身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.56,0:22:57.52,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}神明凛然在上　抛下两难抉择
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.52,0:23:02.11,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不断拷问你我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.11,0:23:07.11,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}几步对错　令我身负百孔千疮
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.11,0:23:10.16,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}形单影只渐行渐远
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.45,0:23:16.62,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}希望碎片　谁人不曾拥有
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.87,0:23:21.21,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}又能作何挣扎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.21,0:23:26.38,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}神明凛然在上　抛下两难抉择
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.38,0:23:31.22,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不断拷问你我
